# COMMENCEMENT DATE CERTIFICATE

This Commencement Date Certificate is entered into by Landlord and Tenant pursuant to Section 2.02 of the deed of lease.

1. DEFINITIONS. In this certificate the following terms have the meanings given to them:

   (a) Landlord: SIP/CREF 6849 Old Dominion, LLC  
   (b) Tenant: Johns Hopkins Community Physicians, Inc.  
   (c) Lease: Deed of Lease dated March 30, 2021  
   (d) Premises: Suite # 300  
   (e) Building Address: 6849 Old Dominion Drive, McLean, VA 22101
